<!-- Possible parameters:
	Name: a unique string identifying the dialog
	TriggerCondition: possible values defined in Client/DALFlashBase/src/com/ea2d/dal/display/events/DialogTriggerEvent.as
	ConditionParam: possible values defined in Client/DALFlashBase/src/com/ea2d/dal/display/events/DialogTriggerEvent.as
	IsBuy: TRUE or FALSE
	IsBuyAndUse: TRUE or FALSE - buy dialog that uses the item immediately
	IsBuyAndEquip: TRUE or FALSE - buy dialog that equips the item immediately
	IsShare: TRUE or FALSE
	Probability: number from 0 to 100
	TitleText: localization id for string to display for dialog title
	Desc1Text: localization id for string to display for top description field
	Desc2Text: localization id for string to display for bottom description field
	YesText: localization id to override the default yes text for buy/share dialog
	NoText: localization id to override the default no text for buy/share dialog
	OfferId: title of the offer in the store catalog to use for the buy dialog (comma separated list in priority order for 3 choice dialog)
	WallPostId: id of the wall post to use for the share dialog
	SoundId: id of the sound to play when this dialog is open if any
	ImageUrl: url to for icon image to display in the dialog, overrides default from offer or wall post image
	LinkageName: linkage name to use for icon image to display (needs to be in asset swf not embedded swc)
	Cooldown: The number of seconds between when 2 dialogs of this type can ever be shown to a user
	OverrideGlobalCooldown: TRUE or FALSE.  Bypass the global cooldown if necessary to show this type of dialog
	MaxTimes: The maximum number of times this type of dialog can be shown to a user
	IsDaily: TRUE or FALSE, whether or not this dialog can only be shown once per day
	MinPlayTime: The minimum amount of time you must have been playing (in seconds) for this to be shown
	StartDate: The first date this can be shown (in the format 1/2/2011 - you must use full year)
	EndDate: The last date this can be shown (in the format 1/2/2011 - you must use full year)
	CooldownAfterMaxCount: How often in seconds the dialog can be shown after max count is reached (default or < 0 means never)
	IsLinkAccountDialog: Whether this is a dialog that includes the ability to link a nucleus account
	IsLargeDialog: Whether this is a large dialog with the ability to show multiple images
	CooldownGroup: Name of cooldown group this is tied to, cooldown specified for that group affects all dialogs in the group
	Comparisons xml node with Comparison nodes containing the following: 
		ComparisonType: possible values defined in Client/DALFlashBase/src/com/ea2d/dal/model/global/dialog/Comparison.as
		ComparePercent: TRUE or FALSE
		CompareAgainst: value to compare against for VALUE_CHANGE trigger
		ChangeRequired: TRUE or FALSE, whether this only triggers if this comparison has just become true
	LaunchIcon xml node with information on icon to be used to launch the dialog
		MinX: minimum x position to spawn at
		MaxX: maximum x posiiton to spawn at
		MinY: minimum y position to spawn at
		MaxY: maximum y position to spawn at
		LinkageName: linkage name to use for the launch icon to display (needs to be in asset swf not embedded swf)
		ImageUrl: url of launch icon to display if loading an external image instead of an art asset in a swf
		ShowDuration: maximum time to show the launch icon in seconds
		RemovalTrigger: Name of trigger condition that will cause the launch icon to be removed
	ItemIds: comma separated list of items to display in this dialog	
-->
